{"tid":1546520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（幫手fc!!!!)追究831新方向！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-06T10:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T02:02:07.000Z","uid":285300,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"84458b472966fdfd338af590388fb06fe6186147","tid":1546520,"uid":285300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:01:24.000Z","msg":"發夢撞到有手足做殮房職員<br />\n佢研究左好耐啲片<br />\n話啲狗831係地鐵站殺左人既話<br />\n因為即時死亡可以唔洗去醫院<br />\n[size=4<span style=\"color: red;\">]所以好大機會直接用港鐵去荔枝角再轉車送去葵涌公眾殮房 （好近</span>）[/size=4]<br />\n火葬前要判斷死因要法醫簽紙 法醫同狗好friend <br />\n所以可以就咁當失蹤人口咁處理唔洗通知家屬<br />\n手足估計既處理屍體時間：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最快9-12號 柴灣 歌連臣角火葬場</span></span><br />\n(因為9號前火葬爐無哂位）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">12號後 葵涌火葬場</span></span><br />\n而長洲火葬場太遠 唔會去個度<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">所以手足提議可以比壓力食環處 要求葵涌公眾殮房公報當日死亡數字！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為手足無連登account所以我代post<br />\n有無更多手足可以幫手fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b09517c100e25145eb5c20d95a58b1851ca7e3","tid":1546520,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=bf24367b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1208fd35d36ef0308601a533fba9c2e676cd2226","tid":1546520,"uid":285300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"自推十次推推推推"},{"pid":"522